org.gridgain.grid
Interface GridCloudResourceShadow

All Superinterfaces:
GridMetadataAware, Serializable
public interface GridCloudResourceShadow
extends GridMetadataAware

When a cloud resource is removed it leaves a shadow. A resource shadow is a read-only snapshot of its last internal state. Resource shadow is available on GridCloudEvent when resource is removed.

Map<String,String> parameters()
